        <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Entity Relationship Model&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; is a model for designing a database. Data is represented as &lt;strong&gt;entities&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; with attributes. Entities are linked by &lt;strong&gt;relations&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</summary>
        
